                    p You can learn Classical Dance here.
        div.card
            h3 Traditional Dance
            div.card-box
                div.card-img
                    img(src="/static/img/download_1.png", alt="Image can't be loaded")
                div.card-content
                    p You can learn Traditional Dance here.
